# language rule content

- Always use English for all content in the project
- This includes:
  - Code comments
  - Documentation
  - Markdown files
  - Variable names
  - Function names
  - Class names
  - File names
  - Commit messages
  - Pull request descriptions
- No exceptions for non-English languages
